pma:database.pma:table: CREATE TABLE `twitter_home_timeline` ( `twitter_user_id` bigint(20) unsigned NOT NULL, `twitter_status_id` bigint(20) unsigned NOT NULL, `favorited` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0', `manual_classification` set('important','not-important','not-important') DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`twitter_user_id`,`twitter_status_id`), KEY `fk_tht_twitter_user_id` (`twitter_user_id`), KEY `fk_tht_twitter_status_id` (`twitter_status_id`), CONSTRAINT `fk_tht_twitter_status_id` FOREIGN KEY (`twitter_status_id`) REFERENCES `twitter_status` (`id`) ON DELETE NO ACTION ON UPDATE NO ACTION, CONSTRAINT `fk_tht_twitter_user_id` FOREIGN KEY (`twitter_user_id`) REFERENCES `twitter_user` (`id`) ON DELETE NO ACTION ON UPDATE NO ACTION ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;
